Description: CDE-style desktop environment for labwc
 NsCDE-Wayland provides a Common Desktop Environment (CDE) inspired
 desktop experience on Wayland using labwc as the compositor.
 .
 Features include a CDE-style front panel, color/font/backdrop
 management, theme generation for labwc/GTK/Qt/Kvantum/Firefox,
 and XDG menu integration.
